## Features

- ?? **Video Detection** ? CNN-based analysis with Grad-CAM heatmaps showing manipulated regions
- ??? **Audio Detection** ? MFCC feature extraction with Random Forest classifier and SHAP explainability
- ?? **Detection History** ? Registered users can save and review past results
- ?? **Guest Mode** ? Try without signing in
- ?? **Firebase Auth** ? Secure login and user management

