## Getting Started

### Backend
```bash
cd IntegriFy/backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

### Frontend
```bash
cd IntegriFy/frontend
# Add your Firebase config to js/firebase.js
npx serve .
```

> Ensure `models/trainedModel.keras` and `models/audio_rf_model.pkl` are present before starting the server.

---

## API Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/health` | Server status |
| `POST` | `/detect/video` | Analyze a video file (`.mp4`, `.mov`, `.avi`) |
| `POST` | `/detect/audio` | Analyze an audio file (`.wav`, `.mp3`) |

